{"tid":1795928,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"BE WATER：「聚如露」、「散如霧」、「行如水」、「硬如冰」","createTime":"2019-12-24T09:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T10:14:46.000Z","uid":335348,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"66c79a927e799c121530d162dd6561a37a2746c9","tid":1795928,"uid":335348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T09:15:42.000Z","msg":"六個月嚟，經常都聽到李小龍名句「Be water」，呢一句成為咗唔少抗爭者行動原則，甚至美國參議員Josh Hawley更以此嚟命名佢最新提出、可以制裁中國同香港政府官員嘅法案。<br />\n<br />\n《金融時報》評論文章，選出咗<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「Be water」</span></strong>係年度字詞之一，以各種水嘅形態形容抗爭者：堵路包圍時<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「聚如露」</span></strong>，防暴到場則<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「散如霧」</span></strong>；遊走橫街小巷時<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「行如水」</span></strong>，正面勇武抗爭時<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「硬如冰」</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n呢一種抗爭哲學由香港擴散到西班牙、智利、黎巴嫩，成為世界各地示威者面對防暴警察時嘅戰術。<br />\n<br />\n香港抗爭舉世矚目，甚至影響各地，奈何歷經半年，香港人失去嘅遠比爭取到嘅多。願流水不息，滴水成浪，終有一日能夠推倒高牆。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YvQXgT7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvQXgT7.jpg&h=30dc5c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原圖來源：financial times / 毛記電視"},{"pid":"d9d23782c4829459bf6cf713a5ca840476d8efdd","tid":1795928,"uid":335348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T09:26:05.000Z","msg":"Proud of HK!!"},{"pid":"ec3b94ee0329706960ec5a09cb314b0fe249225a","tid":1795928,"uid":335348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:14:46.000Z","msg":"願榮光歸香港"}]}